author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Drywall repair finishing tips…I prefill the perimeter with Quick Set 20 because it sets up within an hour. I knock down high spots, lightly sand and use Strait-Flex Crack Tape. This makes the repair strong and after passes with the 6, 10, and 12 inch knives, the wall looks super smooth 🔥#drywall #drywallrepair #bathroomremodel #homerenovation #homerepairtutor
title: Drywall Repair Finishing Tips - #shorts #drywall #homerepairtutor
